raphique, 1888-","Manganaro, 2005, Per la storia della Sicilia bilingue in epoca tardoantica: presbiteri cristiani e superstizione giudaizzante nel contado","Manganaro Perrone, 2006, Epigrafe in greco di IV sec. d.C. di Alesa (Sicilia) in versi e prosa, per la morte di Eirena Philandros, \"carissima a Botis boio-celtico\"","Rizzone, 2009, Iscrizioni tardoantiche da Mineo (CT)",[204,205,205,206,207,208,209],"R46KDTZX","F2GG87EQ","77P5MNIR","XRJWG8D3","6KPB9V5B","P44QBETH",[211,212,213,27,32,36,214,215,214,215,216,217,101],"isic003461","epitaph of gregorios",{"_":5},"sicilia","sicily","unknown","ancient greek",[],{"title":220,"body":221,"divs":222,"editions":247,"images":257,"handnote":258},"ISic003461. Epitaph of Gregorios","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P44QBETH\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P44QBETH\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[ἐν]θάδε κῆτε ὡ ἐν μακαρίᾳ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[μ]νήμῃ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γρηγώριος υἱὸς Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γρηγώριος\">Γρηγώριος\u003C/span> υἱὸς \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πο\">Πο\u003C/span>-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span> του π\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ρ\u003C/span>(εσ)\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">β\u003C/span>(υτέρου) ζήσας ἔτη κβ´ \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[τ(ελ)]ευτᾷ δὲ ἐν \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ\u003C/span>(υρί)\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ῳ\u003C/span> μηνὴ Ἰ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ου\u003C/span>(λίῳ) \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ἰν\u003Cspan class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">δ\u003C/span>(ικτιῶνος) η´ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P44QBETH\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P44QBETH\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[..]ΘΑΔΕΚΗΤΕΩΕΝΜΑΚΑΡΙΑ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[.]ΝΗΜΗ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γρηγώριος υἱὸς Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γρηγώριος\">ΓΡΗΓΩΡΙΟΣ\u003C/span>ΥΙΟΣ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πο\">ΠΟ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΤΟΥΠ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ρ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Β\u003C/span>ΖΗΣΑΣΕΤΗΚΒ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[.]ΕΥΤΑΔΕΕΝ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω\u003C/span>ΜΗΝΗΙ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΙΝ\u003Cspan class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">Δ\u003C/span>Η\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Rizzone 2009, checked against photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Manganaro restores a christogram at the start of the line, which can only be hypothetical\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: \u003Cspan>Rizzone: Πο-|[θή]του; Manganaro πρ(εσ)β(ύτερος) \u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"4\">4: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: ἐν κώ(μη)ͅ Μηνηνίου; ἰου(λίου) or ἰου(νίου) is possible.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>There seems no clear basis on which to decide whether Gregorios or his father was the presbuteros, since the ending is lost in the abbreviation, but it clearly affects the debate regarding celibacy of priests. Manganaro assumed the word referred to Gregorios; Rizzone to his father Po[--]tos. \u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 2004.0665 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 56.1107 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 54.0944 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 2006.0566 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 2005 35-37 fig.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001799\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001799\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro Perrone 2006 92 n.20 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001787\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001787\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzone 2009 431 fig.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>lunate epsilon and sigma, uncial omega, delta with extended hasta, use of supralines.\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[223,226,229,232,235,238,241,244],{"id":224,"html":225},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P44QBETH\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/P44QBETH\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[ἐν]θάδε κῆτε ὡ ἐν μακαρίᾳ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cs