-text=\"Γρηγώριος υἱὸς Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γρηγώριος\">ΓΡΗΓΩΡΙΟΣ\u003C/span>ΥΙΟΣ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Πο\n                    \">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πο\">ΠΟ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΤΟΥΠ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ρ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Β\u003C/span>ΖΗΣΑΣΕΤΗΚΒ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[.]ΕΥΤΑΔΕΕΝ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω\u003C/span>ΜΗΝΗΙ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΙΝ\u003Cspan class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">Δ\u003C/span>Η\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":227,"html":228},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>",{"id":230,"html":231},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Rizzone 2009, checked against photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Manganaro restores a christogram at the start of the line, which can only be hypothetical\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"3\">3: \u003Cspan>Rizzone: Πο-|[θή]του; Manganaro πρ(εσ)β(ύτερος) \u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"4\">4: \u003Cspan>Manganaro: ἐν κώ(μη)ͅ Μηνηνίου; ἰου(λίου) or ἰου(νίου) is possible.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":233,"html":234},"translation","\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>",{"id":236,"html":237},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>There seems no clear basis on which to decide whether Gregorios or his father was the presbuteros, since the ending is lost in the abbreviation, but it clearly affects the debate regarding celibacy of priests. Manganaro assumed the word referred to Gregorios; Rizzone to his father Po[--]tos. \u003C/p>  ",{"id":239,"html":240},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 2004.0665 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 56.1107 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 54.0944 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 2006.0566 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 2005 35-37 fig.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001799\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001799\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro Perrone 2006 92 n.20 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001787\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001787\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzone 2009 431 fig.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001634\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":242,"html":243},"handnote","\u003Cp>lunate epsilon and sigma, uncial omega, delta with extended hasta, use of supralines.\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":245,"